I believe in being treated justly, but I DON'T feel that those of us who have sacrificed to get ahead should pay for those that waste their lives away.  I started out just like them, but I made something of myself.  They should do the same.  Poverty doesn't have to be their future.  They determine that, if they would only work for it.  In America, we aren't guaranteed a lush lifestyle.  Rather...we are guaranteed the opportunity of advancement.  I have yet to meet a person that doesn't have the opportunity to better themselves.  It's time Americans stop making excuses for lazy people.
